data.description: Better than NEW! 3 bedroom, 2 full bathroom home in South Moorhead.  Vaulted ceilings and a kitchen island  make for great upper level entertaining.  Lower level has a family room, 2 bedrooms, nice size laundry area and a full bathroom.  The beautiful grassy yard is perfect for those backyard get togethers.  Call today for your showing - won't last long! Best Yard in town!!!
